summary: The popular Hot File Skyrim SE mod has finally been ported: Absorb dragon souls with a valiant shout and epic build music followed by a cinematic explosion of power. Everything is customizable - vocals can be male, female, or just instrumental. This mod is universally compatible, can be easily installed on new or existing saves
author: Edmond Noir
